             NUMBER OF DEALS (DISCLOSED VALUE IN DOLLARS M)*
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
                  Acquisitions       Joint     Greenfield
                                  ventures    investments     Total
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
Russia            11 (1,167)    285 (9,239)    106 (152)  402  (10,559)
Kazakhstan         0             43 (9,118)     15   (6)   58   (9,124)
Eastern Germany   64 (4,927)      2    (52)     12 (594)   78   (5,573)
