<HEADLINE>
FT  27 SEP 93 / UK Company News: Roxboro
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Roxboro Group, the specialist electronic components maker which plans to
come to the market next month, reported pre-tax profits of Pounds 2.97m for
the six months to July 2. For the year to December 1992 it achieved profits
of Pounds 3.85m.
Mr Harry Tee, chief executive, said the second half had started well.
Turnover amounted to Pounds 22.1m (Pounds 35.7m for 1992).
