<HEADLINE>
FT  27 SEP 93 / World Bank/IMF Meeting: World Bank to announce three-year
loan package to Mexico
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By NANCY DUNNE
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
   WASHINGTON
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
The World Bank will announce a three-year Dollars 1.8bn (Pounds 1.16bn) loan
package to Mexico tomorrow for environmental clean-up and protection, writes
Nancy Dunne in Washington. It will be the bank's largest environmental
facility to a single country.
